---
import TransparentButton from "../buttons/TransparentButton.astro";
---

<main
  class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-5 flex-grow min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center"
>
  <section class="py-6 sm:py-8 md:py-10">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1
        class="font-heading text-2xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-[2.75rem] font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900 to-slate-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text mb-4 md:mb-6 leading-tight"
      >
        <span class="text-blue-600">Zero-Fail</span> AWS Infrastructure<br
          class="hidden sm:block"
        />
        <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-[2.15rem]"
          >When Every Minute of Downtime Costs $5,000+ per minute</span
        >
      </h1>

      <p
        class="font-sans text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-5 md:mb-7 leading-tight mt-2"
      >
        AWS-Certified Solutions Architect who rescued critical enterprise
        deployments after 14+ hours of infrastructure failure
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-3 mb-6 md:mb-8">
        <div
          class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed pl-3 border-l-2 sm:border-l-3 border-blue-500"
        >
          <p>
            Crisis Prevention Architectureâ„¢ methodology developed in
            high-stakes production environments
          </p>
          <ul
            class="mt-2 space-y-1 text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 list-disc list-inside"
          >
            <li>Fixed-price architecture audit ($3,500)</li>
            <li>Production crisis insurance</li>
            <li>Implementation packages from $15,000</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col xs:flex-row gap-3 items-start">
        <TransparentButton
          href="https://cal.com/jrioscloud/45min"
          text="Book Crisis Prevention Assessment"
          class="w-full xs:w-auto px-4 py-3 text-sm sm:text-base font-sans hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
